# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# .claudeignore — Ingenio La Corona
# Archivos que Claude NO debe escanear ni leer.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ─── Credenciales y configuración sensible ───
.env
.env.*
*.env
credentials.json
credentials*.json
**/credentials.json
**/credentials*.json
*.cred
*.credential
**/service-account-key.json
**/google-service-account.json

# ─── Backups y temporales ───
*.bak
*.backup
*.old
*.orig
*~
*.swp
*.swo
*.tmp
temp/
tmp/
**/temp/**
**/tmp/**
~$*

# ─── Archivos comprimidos y binarios ───
*.rar
*.zip
*.7z
*.tar.gz
*.tar
*.gz
*.iso
*.dmg
*.exe
*.dll
*.bin
*.msi
*.pkg
*.deb
*.rpm

# ─── Logs ───
*.log
**/logs/**
**/log/**
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# ─── Dependencias ───
node_modules/
**/node_modules/**
vendor/
**/vendor/**
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
**/__pycache__/

# ─── Base de datos local ───
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
*.db
*.mdf
*.ldf

# ─── Certificados y claves SSH ───
*.pem
*.key
*.cert
*.crt
*.pub
id_rsa
id_dsa
**/.ssh/**

# ─── Archivos de Office con datos sensibles (solo los que contienen datos reales) ───
**/info/*.xlsx
**/data/*.xlsx
!**/plantillas/**
!**/templates/**

# ─── IDE ───
.vscode/
.idea/
*.sublime-workspace
*.sublime-project

# ─── Sistema ───
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store
desktop.ini
*.lnk

# ─── Node-RED credentials ───
**/flows_cred.json
**/flows/**/cred*
**/node_modules/@node-red/**
